public interface IGenericDAO<T,ID extends java.io.Serializable>

Author:
mdean - Not really - copied from Hibernate repository and 2nd edition

All CRUD (create, read, update, delete) basic data access operations are isolated in this interface and shared across all DAO implementations. I have altered this code to include session getting since I am always going to use Hibernate.
